header_text: Commissioning High Voltage Plant, Protection Testing and Secondary Systems?
Commissioning High Voltage Plant, Protection Testing and Secondary Systems?
paragraph_text: AB Tech Services (ABTS) provides industry leading high voltage plant and protection scheme testing, commissioning and maintenance services to asset owners and supply, transmission and generation authorities. ABTS is Australian owned and operated, with the head office based in Brisbane Queensland. Our dedicated team has over 100 years combined experience in the electrical industry and hold trade, tertiary education and Certificate IV in Training and Assessment qualifications. Our significant knowledge and experience within the industry ensures that high voltage plant, protection and control schemes are commissioned and operate compliant, safely and reliably.

ABTS offers onsite testing services adhering to industry best practices and the highest of standards for high voltage electrical installation testing. ABTS also provides consulting services in relation to protection system design, protection scheme evaluation and protection relay evaluation across a multi‐vendor range of products. Our Capabilities, Vendor Experience and Customers are outlined below.

Providing industry leading high voltage plant and protection scheme testing, commissioning and maintenance services to asset owners and supply, transmission and generation authorities throughout Australia.

Our dedicated team is committed to Safety. We are proud of our No Lost Time Injuries rating.
Our Team calls upon 100 years of combined experience in the Power Transmission and Distribution Industry.
We only use the latest technology in the industry to perform our commissioning and testing tasks.
Our team members are highly regarded in the industry and are members of Engineers Association of Australia.
Our work is fully guaranteed as it is our goal to exceed industry best practice. All work is conducted by Industry Professionals.
We know how difficult it can be to take your HV plant and equipment out of service for maintenance. We will build a plan to suit your business.
